---
import Container from '../ui/Container.astro';
---

<section class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-slate-950 text-white border-b border-white/10 relative">
  <Container>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Left Column: Large Statement (5 Cols) -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-6">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-extrabold tracking-[0.2em] text-blue-400 uppercase font-heading bg-blue-500/10 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-blue-500/20">
          THE STARTS DIGITAL DIFFERENCE
        </span>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">
          Strategy, creative, and technical engineering managed as <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-teal-300">one connected growth system.</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="text-slate-300 text-base leading-relaxed">
          Most businesses waste money managing disjointed freelancers, ad agencies, and web developers who pass blame when performance drops. We take single-point responsibility for full-funnel commercial growth.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: 4 Key Differentiators with Dividers (7 Cols) -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-8">
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/80 border border-white/10 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-all flex items-start gap-5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-400 shrink-0 mt-1">
            <span class="font-mono font-bold text-sm">01</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Single-Point Execution Ownership</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">No finger-pointing between your ad media buyer and website developer. We engineer the ads, landing pages, and lead flows in sync.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/80 border border-white/10 hover:border-teal-500/30 transition-all flex items-start gap-5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-teal-500/10 border border-teal-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-teal-400 shrink-0 mt-1">
            <span class="font-mono font-bold text-sm">02</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Commercial Focus Over Vanity Metrics</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">We optimize for actual bank-account revenue, lead volume, and customer acquisition cost—not meaningless impressions or bot likes.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/80 border border-white/10 hover:border-indigo-500/30 transition-all flex items-start gap-5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-indigo-500/10 border border-indigo-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-400 shrink-0 mt-1">
            <span class="font-mono font-bold text-sm">03</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Clean Technical Foundations</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">Custom, light code architectures without bloatware, ensuring fast load speed and clean SEO indexing for long-term compounding growth.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/80 border border-white/10 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-all flex items-start gap-5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-400 shrink-0 mt-1">
            <span class="font-mono font-bold text-sm">04</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Direct Founder Communication</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">Work directly with senior strategists who understand business metrics, supply chains, and market realities across Pakistan and international markets.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
